OL,3,CFamily-run fish and chip shop sold to
OL,4,CUK chain for nearly a million pounds
OL,6,FA family-run fish and chip shop in
OL,7,FGuernsey which closed its doors
OL,8,Fearlier this year has been sold to a
OL,9,Fsmall-scale chain for close to a
OL,10,Fmillion pounds.
OL,12,FBeetons, which shut when its owners,
OL,13,FAndy and Kim Ashplant, retired after
OL,14,F25 years due to increased running
OL,15,Fcosts, will be taken over by Antony
OL,16,FAkathiotis, owner of Merchants, which
OL,17,Fruns two shops in the West Midlands.
OL,19,FAndy Ashplant told ITV News that the
OL,20,Fbusiness had been sold to Mr
OL,21,FAkathiotis for #975,000.
