OL,4,CUK chain for nearly a million pounds
OL,6,FMr Akathiotis says he cannot confirm
OL,7,Fan opening date but that he hoped to
OL,8,Fbe up and running by mid-January.
OL,10,FThe 43-year-old, who has worked in
OL,11,Ffish and chip shops since he was a
OL,12,Fchild, says he plans to move to
OL,13,FGuernsey with his wife and children,
OL,14,Fhaving fallen in love with the island
OL,15,Fon previous visits.
OL,17,FSpeaking about the opportunity to keep
OL,18,FBeetons going as a fish and chip shop,
OL,19,FMr Akathiotis said: "If we'd missed
OL,20,Fout on it, we'd have regretted it."
