OL,6,FHe added: "I love Guernsey and have
OL,7,Falways thought about (opening) a shop
OL,8,Fthere."
OL,10,FThe Merchants boss added that he wants
OL,11,Fto sponsor local charities and invite
OL,12,Fsocial media influencers from the UK
OL,13,Fto help promote independent shops in
OL,14,Fthe island.
OL,16,FMr Akiathiotis says he's "really
OL,17,Flooking forward to getting going" and
OL,18,Fthat "we've still got a lot to learn
OL,19,Fbut we're going to give it a good go."
